Necross/ Splattercannon:
 
"It will take a minute or two to enter the atmosphere and then it should be easy to find their base in no time."
Necross, true to his word.  The minions completed re- entry and soon Necoss broke away from Splattercannon.  He flew along side Splattercannon at a slow pace, both waiting for the other three to catch up then they could all go and fight.
